{"tid":651370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頑童遭17女生圍住吐口水 Miss仲話：大家鼓掌","createTime":"2018-05-03T05:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T00:43:38.000Z","uid":153228,"like":153,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"51bc9353126627ed223168986c539f3b372d899f","tid":651370,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:07:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180503/58143309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180503%2F58143309&d=hAgi6XNAq8QbtBb1FsP%2BSwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=798af0dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180503%2F58143309&h=9e09b1ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180503/58143309</a><br />\n<br />\n中國媒體本周二（1日）流傳一段影片，片中幼稚園女教師竟要學生「以牙還牙，以眼還眼」，要求班上17名女學生，排隊對一名男學生吐口水，每個學生吐完口水後，班上學生還要鼓掌附和讚好。男童家長知道事件後，馬上向當地教育局投訴，並計劃將涉事教師告上法院。涉事張姓女教師兼幼稚園園長已被停職。<br />\n<br />\n河南平頂山一間幼稚園的CCTV片段可見，一名身穿橙色運動套裝，自稱是張老師的女子說：「張老師今天就要來處理一個小朋友」，指一名男學生，在女廁外的樓梯上向女生吐口水，於是着班上共17名女生「我們班女生排着隊，一起去吐他」、「但是不要吐太多唾沫在他身上」，還要「每一個小朋友吐完之後，我們都給她鼓掌」。然後就整班女生推開椅子起來，排隊向男學生，一個一個吐口水，期間男生站在課室，默默承受。<br />\n完事後，張老師還問班上女生：「他（被吐口水男生）現在敢不敢吐我們班小朋友了」、「他哭了沒有啊」、「因為他很難受，對不對」，班上女學童連聲和應。<br />\n男童的家長知情後，馬上向當地教育局投訴。可是，張老師指自己只是做了一個模擬，並沒有真的讓女同學把口水吐到男孩的身上，只是說在這個批判的過程中想讓孩子知道這個事情是不對的。市教育局和新華區教育局調查事件後，下令要張老師停職，並要求該幼兒園整改。<br />\n不過，男童家長並不滿意，決定將幼兒園和涉事教師起訴到法院，讓法院給一個法律上公平的處理結果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180502/large/1525272742_5e4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180502%2Flarge%2F1525272742_5e4f.jpg&h=c83faae1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f77be42c7a53c3b37d8a241049333b44f80f4e1","tid":651370,"uid":65429,"like":262,"dislike":12,"score":250,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"我都想俾個17個少女瘋狂向我吐口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8eb0d12ddd9393238df0d39e68e035dfb17b2ee","tid":651370,"uid":46587,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"睇錯向十七女生吐口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d06020d186181eec5ccde60807ffeeca2fe3f2","tid":651370,"uid":8048,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"無家教等老師教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba21b0ff794b30a5119e1e349503e137a34469b4","tid":651370,"uid":146917,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"7f77be42c7a53c3b37d8a241049333b44f80f4e1","tid":651370,"uid":65429,"like":262,"dislike":12,"score":250,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"我都想俾個17個少女瘋狂向我吐口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:17:09.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最好打埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012e17176095004f5652f4b8fdcec170c3ba00e8","tid":651370,"uid":132038,"like":200,"dislike":9,"score":191,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:17:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"738f2593b4d8e08c4f36f30f9976e5f4efebcc80","tid":651370,"uid":71166,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:17:36.000Z","msg":"其實呢個女老師係教緊真係社會實況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af0f7f5f4792f0c5336cec90c1d9a7e763f55e7","tid":651370,"uid":3454,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"以牙還牙，以眼還眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a929d5a5d2d33900a403887254b5db85c69b83ac","tid":651370,"uid":176366,"like":2,"dislike":28,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T05:18:18.